              "free_text": [
                " The 14UD tandem accelerator."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A target of Hf-178 was approx. 100 mug/cm**2 in",
                "thickness, evaporated onto a approx. 15-mug/cm**2",
                "carbon foil backing. The backing faced upstream,",
                "so that the evaporation residue(ERs) angular",
                "distribution would not be affected by passage of the",
                "ERs through the carbon foil."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".ERs were detected in a 35-mm diameter Si-",
                "surface barrier detector, located behind a compact",
                "velocity filter, which separated beam particles from",
                "the ERs.",
                "Cross sections were determined making use of two",
                "monitor detectors, in which elastic scattering from the",
                "Hf-172 was clearly identified."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Coincidence measurements of the evaporation",
                "residues and prompt gamma-rays should allow",
                "identification of the fusion products from reactions",
                "with the small isomeric component in the existing",
                "targets."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SITA"
